{
  "page": "Minisa Tully",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Whent\" title=\"House Whent\"><img alt=\"House Whent.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/7d/House_Whent.svg/50px-House_Whent.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/7d/House_Whent.svg/75px-House_Whent.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/7d/House_Whent.svg/100px-House_Whent.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Lady</span><br />Minisa Tully</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tully\" title=\"House Tully\"><img alt=\"House Tully.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/61/House_Tully.svg/50px-House_Tully.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/61/House_Tully.svg/75px-House_Tully.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/61/House_Tully.svg/100px-House_Tully.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Minisa_Whent_by_Elia_Mervi.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Minisa Whent by Elia Mervi.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/62/Minisa_Whent_by_Elia_Mervi.jpg/350px-Minisa_Whent_by_Elia_Mervi.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"/images/6/62/Minisa_Whent_by_Elia_Mervi.jpg 1.5x\" /></a><div>Minisa, by Elia Mervi</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nMinisa Whent</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\nLady of <a href=\"/index.php/Riverrun\" title=\"Riverrun\">Riverrun</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Whent\" title=\"House Whent\">House Whent</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tully\" title=\"House Tully\">House Tully</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Rivermen\" title=\"Rivermen\">Rivermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_250_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">250&#160;AC</a> or before<sup id=\"cite_ref-Cal_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Cal-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Harrenhal\" title=\"Harrenhal\">Harrenhal</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiaf_minisa_whent.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiaf_minisa_whent.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_271_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">271</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_278_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">278&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Cal_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Cal-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Riverrun\" title=\"Riverrun\">Riverrun</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiaf_minisa_whent.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiaf_minisa_whent.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Spouse</th><td>\nLord <a href=\"/index.php/Hoster_Tully\" title=\"Hoster Tully\">Hoster Tully</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li>Two sons</li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn Tully</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lysa_Arryn\" title=\"Lysa Arryn\">Lysa Tully</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Edmure_Tully\" title=\"Edmure Tully\">Edmure Tully</a></li><li>Son</li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i> (appendix)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (appendix)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Minisa Tully</b>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> née <b>Whent</b>, was a noblewoman of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Whent\" title=\"House Whent\">House Whent</a> who became the wife of <a href=\"/index.php/Hoster_Tully\" title=\"Hoster Tully\">Hoster Tully</a>, Lord of <a href=\"/index.php/Riverrun\" title=\"Riverrun\">Riverrun</a>, and the mother of <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lysa_Arryn\" title=\"Lysa Arryn\">Lysa</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Edmure_Tully\" title=\"Edmure Tully\">Edmure</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance_and_Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance and Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Family\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Family</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Minisa_Tully&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The always calm Minisa had soft hands and a warm smile.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> <a href=\"/index.php/Brynden_Tully\" title=\"Brynden Tully\">Brynden Tully</a> states that his niece <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn</a>, believed by many to be pretty,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos80.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos80.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup> resembles Minisa in her cheekbones and jaw.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok7.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok7.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup> Catelyn's elder daughter, <a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa</a>, has high cheekbones as well.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot7.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot7.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Minisa_Tully&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Minisa was born into <a href=\"/index.php/House_Whent\" title=\"House Whent\">House Whent</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Lords_of_Harrenhal\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lords of Harrenhal\">Lords of Harrenhal</a>, and she wed their liege, <a href=\"/index.php/Hoster_Tully\" title=\"Hoster Tully\">Hoster Tully</a>, the Lord of <a href=\"/index.php/Riverrun\" title=\"Riverrun\">Riverrun</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Paramount_of_the_Trident\" title=\"Lord Paramount of the Trident\">Lord Paramount of the Trident</a>. Minisa's first two children were sons who died in infancy,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup> but her later children <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lysa_Arryn\" title=\"Lysa Arryn\">Lysa</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Edmure_Tully\" title=\"Edmure Tully\">Edmure</a> grew to adulthood. Minisa died in childbirth with her fourth son, who also died shortly after.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The sept of <a href=\"/index.php/Riverrun\" title=\"Riverrun\">Riverrun</a> is located in Minisa's gardens.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Minisa_Tully&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Minisa_Tully&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Hoster_Tully\" title=\"Hoster Tully\">Hoster Tully</a> still misses his late wife. Ailing and feverish, Hoster mistakenly calls his daughter <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn</a> by Minisa's name.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok7.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok7.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Minisa_Tully&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Brynden</b>: <a href=\"/index.php/Hoster_Tully\" title=\"Hoster Tully\">He</a> misses her still. You have her face. I can see it in your cheekbones, and your jaw ...<br />\n<b>Catelyn</b>: You remember more of her than I do. It has been a long time.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok7.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok7.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Brynden_Tully\" title=\"Brynden Tully\">Brynden Tully</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn Stark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Lady Minisa Tully had died in childbed, trying to give Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Hoster_Tully\" title=\"Hoster Tully\">Hoster</a> a second son. The baby had perished with her, and afterward some of the life had gone out of Father. She was always so calm, Catelyn thought, remembering her mother's soft hands, her warm smile. If she had lived, how different our lives might have been.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn Stark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Minisa_Tully&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire\">A Song of Ice and Fire</a></i> has not mentioned Minisa's relation to other members of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Whent\" title=\"House Whent\">House Whent</a>.   \n</p>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Tull